metadata.name: Blackingboy
metadata.description: He is named Blackingboy, another figure that is within me. he has everything that I don't have, if I am a quiet person, he is an arrogant person, a king, who seeks to conquer the world and has all the abilities in the world. Yes, he is an imaginary figure that I created because I am always pessimistic about the life I have, so he is a person who can make it happen.
